com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306

Class ProductSegmentation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306.ProductSegmentation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ProductSegmentation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Segmentations used to create products. Within a product template, for each segmentation, a product will be created for the combination of all other segments within other segmentations.

    For example, a product with 3 segmentations with only 1 segment for each will produce 1 x 1 x 1 = 1 product. A product with 3 segmentations with 2 segments for each will produce 2 x 2 x 2 = 8 products.
